        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Muslim Americans in Public Service (MAPS) invites its members, allies, and leaders from across all branches of government to come together for our 5th Annual Summer DC Networking Event on Capitol Hill on July 17th.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": null,
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1,
        "textFormat": 0,
        "textStyle": ""
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "MAPS is dedicated to supporting the career, workplace, and community development of current, aspiring, and former Muslim American public servants and serving as a catalyst, resource, and force multiplier for other groups that represent and support them. The Summer Networking event is our premier annual gathering of approximately 300 members of the MAPS community, from newly arrived interns on Capitol Hill to tenured members of the Senior Executive Service and everyone in between. We look forward to seeing you!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": null,
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1,
        "textFormat": 0,
        "textStyle": ""
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "‍",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "RSVP via the Luma event link below, where you can login using your MAPS-registered email via the top right corner from the Luma event page: ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 2,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "https://luma.com/maps-kr0k",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": null,
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "version": 3,
            "fields": {
              "linkType": "custom",
              "newTab": false,
