        "textStyle": ""
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Not a Member yet? Join MAPS National as members, associate members, or affiliates for free via https://mapsnational.org/join, where you can support MAPS' mission of facilitating the career, community, and workplace development of Muslim American public servants.",
